  "title": "Structure of the complex between human T-cell receptor, viral peptide and HLA-A2.",
  "journal": "Nature",
  "year": 1996,
  "authors": "Garboczi DN, Ghosh P, Utz U, Fan QR, Biddison WE, Wiley DC."
